88140b992026c7f6e6af3b737203f06a3947e9ecb1809e7fbf24a739fc28a19a797ac7c3b9f47b5dd84c2b18f344471ac6f4cd25785fa66267073f832aa800f2  0001-mkcal-Add-optional-support-for-building-against-Qt6.patch
"
